description:
Park Min Gyeom is a human with a disease that makes him produce excess blood. Kim Chun Sam is a half-vampire who needs blood to live. So begins an unusual symbiotic relationship between &quot;predator&quot; and &quot;prey.&quot;

[b][u]Polish / Polski:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]Park Min Gyeom jest człowiekiem cierpiącym na chorobę, przez kt&oacute;rą jego ciało produkuje nadmierne ilości krwi. Kim Chun Sam jest dhampirem, kt&oacute;ry potrzebuje krwi by przeżyć. Tak rozpoczyna się niezwykła symbioza pomiędzy &quot;drapieżnikiem&quot; i &quot;ofiarą&quot;.[/spoiler]

&quot;Happiness does not exist for gay men who fall for straight men.
I'm happy just being by his side &mdash; was what I was thinking up until&hellip;&quot;

Sakisaka, stationed in the second Sales Division, has an unrequited love for Toujou, his directing senpai. He had no intention of confessing his feelings. However, Toujou has been awfully touchy-feely lately&hellip; Is there a glimmer of hope? Please don't let it be a misunderstanding! Which path will these vexing feelings flow down to?

Every Tuesday night, a mysterious man named &quot;Itou&quot; visits Kyosuke, a prostitute, and talks to him about silly things until dawn. One day, he brings a briefcase full of money and tries to give it to Kyosuke, telling him that he wants him to quit his job and do something he truly wants to do, however&hellip;

[b][u]Polish / Polski:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]W każdą wtorkową noc Kyosuke, męska prostytutka jest wynajmowany przez tajemniczego Pana Itou i spędza z nim noc na rozmowie o wszystkim i o niczym. Pewnego wtorku Pan Itou pojawia się z walizką pełną pieniędzy i daje ją Kyosuke, aby ten m&oacute;gł odejść z zawodu i zaczął robić w życiu to, na co tylko ma ochotę. Tak zaczyna się ta zatopiona w p&oacute;łmroku historia związku dw&oacute;ch mężczyzn, przepełniona wonią prochu i krwi, w kt&oacute;rej krok po kroku odkrywamy prawdziwą naturę bohater&oacute;w.

Cheese! Best Selection FC collection of 6 different works by popular mangaka, chosen by Kitagawa Miyuki.

1) Shinayaka ni Kizutsuite Love 2 by Kitagawa Miyuki
&quot;I'm not needed anymore.&quot;

2) Sora no Shizuku by Nakahara Migiwa
&quot;It's because I've fallen in love with you.&quot;

3) Maruhi no Namida by Fujiwara Yoshiko
&quot;I want to die if it's going to be like this.&quot;

4) IB Kei! by Yoshinaga Noriko
&quot;I want to be hugged by him.&quot;

5) Kimi no Yaiba ga Mune wo Tsukisasu by Osakabe Mashin
&quot;I can't reach her.&quot;

6) Dokidoki, Shisugi by Shimaki Ako
&quot;You've always been special, and I've wanted you.&quot;

1. Dakedo Happy Paradise ~Side Story~ &quot;Anyways Happy Holidays&quot;

2. Angel Love Song
Mizuho is a young girl who just had an argument with her boyfriend, Kei-chan. On the way home, she met a guy with a guitar from the greenhouse who called himself Tenshi. Mizuho took him home and asked him to form a group for the competition to win a cruise dinner so she could make up with Kei-chan. So will Mizuho get back together with her boyfriend, or will something else spark? It was also included in Bloody Kiss v1 tankoubon (2006).

By Salva Nos Scans:

Chika is a high school girl in her 3rd semester of 10th grade, who seems to have no luck on finding love. But before she knew it, she began to care about her classmate Kyohara. A book of serious love lessons.

Includes &quot;The Best Summer&quot; and &quot;The Ringing Bell&quot;

&quot;Revenge is a dish best served cold.&quot;

3 years ago Tomoko confessed to her crush, but was rejected. On her way to the meeting point, she met a geeky guy who asked her to go out with him.

How will their story conclude?

&quot;But suddenly, I had a little sister. That was the problem.&quot;

After her father's remarriage, Sachi suddenly has a new stepsister, Ayari. At first, their interactions are awkward and very brief. However, they soon discover a shared love... of food?

Sachi eventually discovers Ayari's passion for cooking, and the two step-sisters soon begin to bond over Ayari's delicious cooking, and begin to overcome the barriers that had once kept them apart. While their parents are away on their honeymoon, they learn to cope with their differences and bond over a seemingly insignificant thing.

&quot;A special human girl is born once every one thousand years, and the one that marries her will become the one true king.&ldquo;

Ever since Shin Jiahn and Yiahn&rsquo;s mother passed away, the two have become different and distant people. When Yiahn is kidnapped to become the mysterious Goblin Bride, though, Jiahn vows to bring Yiahn back home no matter what. Even if it means venturing through the land of human-eating monsters ruled by four cruel brothers &mdash; who all aim to become king by taking the hand of the Goblin Bride for their own.

From the author of Flow, on LINE.

From Perfect Illusions:

&quot;I can't help but fall in love with that guy. But he is a playboy. Then why can't I get my eyes off him? Why is my heart racing wildly?&quot;

When high school year 1 student, Yajima Konomi, fall in love with her classmate, Gonshou, a true love relationship starts. An emotionally-described senseful story of a young girl.

&quot;I love Nii-chan. Always stay by my side.&quot;
The beloved step-brother Shinichirou, who moved out when he started college - returned home shabby, one year after quitting college!! Sui, who looked up to him since childhood, wants to spend time with him, but for some reason Shinichirou is blunt and cold - even though he kissed Sui one year before, so why...!?
Not only secret love between, but a love tied together through the undesired but inseparable bonds of family.

Also compiled with &quot;A Novelist's Love!&quot;
